    <h2>The Team</h2>
    <div class="portlet_content">
        <li>
            <strong>Subhash</strong>
            and <strong>Shenuja</strong>, partners in life and crime, decided to perform an experiment in education when they started Schoolarly. They set out to answer the question - "What happens when you provide the best of communication tools to a bunch of enthusiastic kids?" and they are happy with the results so far. They live in Kochi, India with their 3 year-old son whose endless questions keep them busy when they are not programming
        </li>
